ard-nominations-1067879/item/feature-motion-picture-best-contemporary-makeup-1067899 |title=Makeup Artists and Hair Stylists Guild Awards: 'Darkest Hour,' 'Wonder' Lead Feature Nominees |first=Carolyn |last=Giardina |website=[[Deadline Hollywood]] |date=January 5, 2018 |accessdate=January 5, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"3\"| [[Motion Picture Sound Editors]]\n| rowspan=\"3\"| February 18, 2018\n| Best Sound Editing: Music in a Feature Film\n| {{sortname|Cam|McLaughlin|nolink=1}}, {{sortname|Rob|Hegedus|nolink=1}}, {{sortname|Dustin|Harris|nolink=1}}\n| {{nom}}\n| rowspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2018/02/motion-picture-sound-editors-golden-reel-awards-mpse-dunkirk-blade-runner-2049-game-of-thrones-1202294296/ |title=\"\u2018Dunkirk\u2019, \u2018Blade Runner 2049\u2019 Take Home Top Honors At MPSE Golden Reel Awards \u2013 Complete Winners List\" |first=Dino-Ray |last=Ramos |website=[[Deadline Hollywood]] |date=February 18, 2018 |accessdate=June 26, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Golden Reel Award for Outstanding Achievement in Sound Editing - Dialogue and ADR for Feature Film|Best Sound Editing: Dialogue and ADR in a Feature Film]]\n| {{sortname|Nathan|Robitaille}}, {{sortname|Nelson|Ferreira|Nelson Ferreira (sound editor)}}, {{sortname|Jill|Purdy|nolink=1}}\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Sound Editing: Sound Effects and Foley in a Feature Film\n| {{sortname|Nathan|Robitaille}}, {{sortname|Tyler|Witham|nolink=1}}, {{sortname|Dashen|Naidoo|nolink=1}}, {{sortname|Kevin|Howard|nolink=1}}, {{sortname|Alex|Bullick|nolink=1}}, {{sortname|Steve|Bain|nolink=1}}, {{sortname|Pete|Persaud|nolink=1}}, {{sortname|Gina|Gyles|nolink=1}}\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\"| [[National Society of Film Critics]]\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[2017 National Society of Film Critics Awards|January 6, 2018]]\n| [[National Society of Film Critics Award for Best Actress|Best Actress]]\n| {{sortname|Sally|Hawkins}}\n| {{won}}\n| rowspan=\"2\" s