206214943/https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/aarp-the-magazine-celebrates-the-winners-for-the-17th-annual-movies-for-grownups-awards-in-los-angeles-300593984.html|archivedate=February 6, 2018|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n|-\n| Best Supporting Actor\n| {{sortname|Richard|Jenkins}}\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Director\n| rowspan=\"2\" | {{sortname|Guillermo|del Toro}}\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Screenwriter\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"13\"| [[Academy Awards]]\n| rowspan=\"13\"| [[90th Academy Awards|March 4, 2018]]\n| [[Academy Award for Best Picture|Best Picture]]\n| {{sortname|Guillermo|del Toro}} and {{sortname|J.|Miles Dale}}\n| {{won}}\n| rowspan=\"13\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/2018 |title=The 90th Academy Awards (2018) Nominees and Winners |accessdate=March 5, 2018|publisher=[[Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences|Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences (AMPAS)]] |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180305111625/http://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/2018|archivedate=March 5, 2018}}</ref><br><ref>{{cite news|url=http://oscar.go.com/nominees/best-picture/the-shape-of-water-2|title=The Shape of Water: Best Picture \u2013 Oscar Nominees 2018|accessdate=March 5, 2018|publisher=Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences (AMPAS)|url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180309132113/http://oscar.go.com/nominees/best-picture/the-shape-of-water-2|archivedate=March 9, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Academy Award for Best Director|Best Director]]\n| {{sortname|Guillermo|del Toro}}\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Academy Award for Best Actress|Best Actress]]\n| {{sortname|Sally|Hawkins}}\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Academy Award for Best Supporting Actor|Best Supporting Actor]]\n| {{sortname|Richard|Jenkins}}\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Academy Award for Best Supporting Actress|Best Supporting Actress]]\n| {{sortname|Octavia|Spencer}}\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Academy Award for Best Original Screenp