da Jones]], President of the [[Detroit City Council]]\n|-\n|{{flagcountry|UK}}\n|[[Boris Johnson]], [[Prime Minister of the United Kingdom]] <br>[[Charles, Prince of Wales|Charles]], [[Prince of Wales]]<br>[[Matt Hancock]], [[Secretary of State for Health and Social Care]]<br>[[Nadine Dorries]], [[Department of Health and Social Care|Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State]]<br>[[Alister Jack]], [[Secretary of State for Scotland]]\n|\n|-\n|{{flagcountry|United Nations}}\n|[[David Beasley]], Executive Director of the [[World Food Programme]]\n|Align=center|\n|-\n|{{flagcountry|European Union}}\n|[[Michel Barnier]], [[Continuing United Kingdom relationship with the European Union|Head of the UK Task Force]]\n|Align=center|\n|-\n| colspan=\"3\" |Source:<ref name=\"USA Today\"/><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://riotimesonline.com/brazil-news/brazil/politics-brazil/general-heleno-tests-positive-for-coronavirus/ |title=Brazil's Cabinet Security Chief Tests Positive for Coronavirus |date=19 March 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-03-21/burkina-faso-mines-minister-tests-positive-for-coronavirus|title=Burkina Faso Mines Minister Tests Positive for Coronavirus|date=21 March 2020|work=Bloomberg.com|access-date=21 March 2020|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=#Coronavirus : Franck Riester, le ministre de la Culture, test\u00e9 positif mais \"en forme\" (cabinet) |url=https://twitter.com/afpfr/status/1237090636760854528 |website=Twitter |publisher=Agence France-Presse |accessdate=9 March 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Menhub Budi Karya Sumadi positif COVID-19 |url=https://www.antaranews.com/berita/1356658/menhub-budi-karya-sumadi-positif-covid-19|language=id |accessdate=14 March 2020 |work=Antara News |date=14 March 2020}}</ref><ref>[https://agenciabrasil.ebc.com.br/saude/noticia/2020-03/em-quarentena-nestor-forster-tem-resultado-positivo-para-o-covid-19 Agenciabrasil.ebc.comb.br: Em quarentena, Nestor Forster tem resultado posi