gia House of Representatives]] {{Composition bar compact|1|180|hex=red}}<ref>Matthew Gambill, District 15</ref><br>[[Georgia State Senate]] {{Composition bar compact|5|56|hex=red}}<ref>[[Brandon Beach]], District 21<br>[[Kay Kirkpatrick]], District 32<br>[[Nikema Williams]], District 39<br>[[Lester Jackson]], District 2<br>[[Bruce Thompson (Georgia politician)|Bruce Thompson]], District 14</ref><br>[[Wisconsin State Assembly]] {{Composition bar compact|1|99|hex=red}}<ref>[[David Bowen (Wisconsin politician)|David Bowen]], District 10</ref><br>[[Connecticut House of Representatives]] {{Composition bar compact|1|151|hex=red}}<ref>[[Jane Garibay]], District 60</ref><br>[[Colorado Senate|Colorado State Senate]] {{Composition bar compact|1|35|hex=red}}<ref>[[Jim Smallwood]], District 4</ref><br>[[Colorado House of Representatives]] {{Composition bar compact|1|65|hex=red}}<ref>[[Dafna Michaelson Jenet]], District 30</ref><br>[[Hawaii Senate|Hawaii State Senate]] {{Composition bar compact|1|25|hex=red}}<ref>[[Clarence Nishihara]], District 17</ref><br>[[Louisiana House of Representatives]] {{Composition bar compact|1|105|hex=black}}<ref>[[Reggie Bagala]], District 54</ref><br>[[New Jersey General Assembly]] {{Composition bar compact|1|80|hex=red}}<ref>[[Clinton Calabrese]], District 36</ref><br>[[Oklahoma Senate|Oklahoma State Senate]] {{Composition bar compact|1|48|hex=red}}<ref>Paul Rosino, District 45</ref><br>[[Oklahoma House of Representatives]] {{Composition bar compact|1|101|hex=red}}<ref>Jason Lowe, District 97</ref><br>[[Missouri House of Representatives]] {{Composition bar compact|1|163|hex=red}}<ref>[[Joe Runions]], District 37</ref><br>[[Michigan House of Representatives]] {{Composition bar compact|2|110|hex=red}}<ref>Tyrone Carter, District 6<br>[[Karen Whitsett]], District 9</ref><br>{{Composition bar compact|1|110|hex=black}}<ref>[[Isaac Robinson (politician)|Isaac Robinson]], District 4</ref><br>[[South Dakota House of Representatives]] {{Composition bar co