akov Litzman]], Minister of Health\n|Jeremy Issacharoff, Ambassador of Israel to Germany\n|-\n| {{flagcountry|ITA}}\n|  \n|[[Nicola Zingaretti]], President of [[Lazio]]<br>[[Alberto Cirio]], President of [[Piedmont]]<br>[[Fulvio Centoz]], Mayor of [[Aosta]]<br>[[Gianluca Galimberti]], Mayor of [[Cremona]]<br>[[Alessandro Tambellini]], Mayor of [[Lucca]]<br>[[Patrizia Barbieri]], Mayor of [[Piacenza]]\n|-\n| {{flagcountry|MEX}}\n|\n|[[Omar Fayad]], [[List of Governors of Hidalgo|Governor of Hidalgo]]<br>[[Francisco Dom\u00ednguez Servi\u00e9n]], [[Governor of Quer\u00e9taro]]<br>[[Ad\u00e1n Augusto L\u00f3pez Hern\u00e1ndez]], [[Governor of Tabasco]]<br>Silvia Guillermina Rold\u00e1n Fern\u00e1ndez, Secretary of Health, [[Tabasco|State of Tabasco]]\n|-\n| {{flagcountry|MAR}}\n|[[Abdelkader Aamara]], [[Ministry of Equipment, Transport and Logistics (Morocco)|Minister of Equipment, Transport and Logistics]]\n|\n|-\n| {{flagcountry|MON}}\n|[[Albert II, Prince of Monaco|Albert II]], [[Prince of Monaco]]\n|\n|-\n|{{flagcountry|Nigeria}}\n|[[Abba Kyari (politician)|Abba Kyari]], [[Chief of Staff to the President (Nigeria)|Chief of Staff to the President]]\n|\n|-\n| {{flagcountry|NOR}}\n|[[Torbj\u00f8rn R\u00f8e Isaksen]], [[Minister of Labour and Social Inclusion]]\n|\n|-\n| {{flagcountry|PHI}}\n|[[Eduardo A\u00f1o]], [[Secretary of the Interior and Local Government (Philippines)|Secretary of the Interior and Local Government]]<br>[[Leonor Briones]], [[Secretary of Education (Philippines)|Secretary of Education]]\n|[[Rebecca Ynares]], [[Governor of Rizal]]<br>Ferdinand V. Estrella, Mayor of [[Baliuag, Bulacan|Baliuag]]<br>Philip Caesar P. Crispino, Mayor of [[Caba, La Union|Caba]]<br>Bernardita Catalla, Ambassador of the Philippines to Lebanon<ref>{{cite news |title=PH envoy to Lebanon dies of COVID-19 complications |url=https://news.abs-cbn.com/overseas/04/02/20/ph-envoy-to-lebanon-dies-of-covid-19-complications |accessdate=2 April 2020 |work=ABS-CBN News |date=2 April 20